             =-=-=-=-=-=-=-=- Pech -=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=

Pech are creatures of the plane of elemental Earth, though some dwell in the
material plane of man.  They dwell in dark places and work on stone. Pech
are thin and have long arms and legs.  Their broad hands and feet are
excellent for bracing and employing tools to work stone.  They have pale,
yellowish skin and red or reddish brown hair.  Their flesh is nearly as hard
as granite.  They have large eyes with no pupils.

Dex: Below Avg    Str: High          Con: High
Int: Avg          Wis: Below Avg     Char: Below Avg

Sight: Dark Vision
Hp Regen: Above Avg
Sp Regen: Nil
Natural Weaponry: Earth attacks
Natural Armour: Very High
Ambidexterity: No
Innate spells/skills: High
Exp Modifier: Low
Physical Resistance: Above Avg

